# Docs & Plans

- PRD/TDD are source of truth; bump version notes in Document Control when changing them.
- Implementation plans live in `docs/plans/` with checkbox tasks.
- Do not invent new product scope in plans without updating PRD/TDD first (ask user).
- Wave detail changelogs live in `docs/changelogs/`; summary in root `CHANGELOG.md`.
- Keep Admin↔API mapping aligned with PRD §15 when documenting demos.
